Monday. Chang scored 3-6, 6-7 (7-4), 6-4, 6-4, 6-3 victory. ; Photo, COLOR, 
(Orange County Edition) Michael Chang of Placentia returns a forehand in his 
comeback victory over Austria's Horst Skoff, giving the United States a 3-2 
win.; Photo, Chang vents his emotions while sweeping both sets after his Davis 
Cup match resumed. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
