<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fidelity National Financial Inc.: The Irvine-based title insurance underwriter 
reported that its net income for the third fiscal quarter rose 11% to $1.9 
million from $1.7 million for the comparable 1989 period. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue for the quarter ended July 31 was up 3% to $46.9 million from $45.6 
million. For the nine-month period, net income totaled $3.6 million, up 38% 
from $2.6 million a year earlier. Revenue rose 15% to $133.9 million from 
$116.6 million. 
</P>
</TEXT>
