Chart, SAUDI OIL SITES AND IRAQI AIR POWER, JUAN THOMASSIE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Analysis 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SAUDI ARABIA -- DEFENSE; MILITARY STRATEGY; HUSSEIN, SADDAM; THREATS; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; MILITARY 
CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; OIL -- PERSIAN 
GULF; OIL -- SAUDI ARABIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092590-0071 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 282773 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 25, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
