<TEXT>
<P>
Donald R. Carter and Bob L. Pugh of CIGNA Financial Services Company have 
earned certified financial planner accreditation. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Appointment 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092590-0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 282961 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 25, 1990, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 9A; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
