</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fashion model Lesly Brown, the wife of "Wheel of Fortune" host Pat Sajak, has 
given birth to a boy. 
</P>
<P>
Patrick Michael James Sajak weighed 7 pounds at birth Saturday at an 
undisclosed Los Angeles-area hospital, Sajak spokesman Bob Burton said Monday. 
</P>
<P>
It was the couple's first child. Sajak, 43, and Brown, 25, were married in 
January. 
</P>
